# MVP auth and OAuth (template)

- **Skill:** Read `.cursor/skills/mvp-paas-auth-oauth/SKILL.md` for the full checklist (reusable for every new MVP).
- **Deploy:** After changing OAuth env vars, run `.\scripts\oauth-setup-render.ps1` (sets Render + migrates + deploy) or `.\scripts\nanoclaw-deploy.ps1 -AppName <app>`.
- **Google Console:** Redirect URI = `https://<BACKEND_URL>/api/auth/google/callback`; JavaScript origins = production `FRONTEND_URL` (exact URL, often team Vercel hostname).
- **Vercel:** `API_BACKEND_URL` + `JWT_SECRET` via `vercel-env-set-api.ps1` for team projects.
